{"tid":1661532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】牧師引述陳同佳稱願到台灣自首","createTime":"2019-10-18T07:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T14:57:43.000Z","uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"67ce00307336c1fc39a4673de14e344e21e7c76d","tid":1661532,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:08:46.000Z","msg":"觸發政府修訂《逃犯條例》的台灣殺人案，疑犯陳同佳預計下星期三刑滿出獄。聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴引述陳同佳表示，願意到台灣自首。<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌在台灣殺害女友潘曉穎的陳同佳，因洗黑錢案在港服刑，預料下星期三刑滿出獄。多次到壁屋監獄探望陳同佳的牧師管浩鳴指，陳同佳向他表示，出獄後想先與家人團聚一段短時間，再去台灣自首，希望為自己做過的事負責。<br />\n<br />\n管浩鳴又指，陳同佳見到因他而起的反修例風波，覺得不開心。管浩鳴又指陳同佳曾與台灣律師談過，對方認為自首加上年輕，判死刑的機會不大。"},{"pid":"86baf557af5ad2ed03bef5d7875ac03e20cf523d","tid":1661532,"uid":9964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"耶穌感化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a7c61c91ed45b5c350292c8582ad0b5dc44799","tid":1661532,"uid":31773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:25:20.000Z","msg":"陳同佳比林奠好一百倍"},{"pid":"7ee2e42683a7be25bd41515c85f9b32f4bbe38cc","tid":1661532,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f5a7c61c91ed45b5c350292c8582ad0b5dc44799","tid":1661532,"uid":31773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:25:20.000Z","msg":"陳同佳比林奠好一百倍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:26:03.000Z","msg":"陳同佳害一個人<br />\n林鄭害全香港人"},{"pid":"ede10ed4efe3b7c677f7332fe82be4661cddcb21","tid":1661532,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"希望判佢死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5b3d36afa202827e4ba63a1299df153da685a9","tid":1661532,"uid":65738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:31:19.000Z","msg":"管浩鳴<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04124126/sdfasfawefawefawfgef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2